  "title": "Haimiya-senpai wa Kowakute Kawaii",
  "description": "At my high school, Haimiya-senpai is feared by all and considered too scary. This is apparently due to her intimidating appearance and blunt way of speaking... and those sparkling piercings! The long, gray wolf-cut hair! Even her Kansai accent is intimidating!!!\nBut for some reason, this scary senpai treats me kindly...?\nAs \"scary\" turns into \"cute,\" this scary (heart-pounding) senpai rom-com begins!",
